column17:
Samsung Note 800 N8000 Deep Grey:
The Samsung Galaxy Note 800 runs on Android Ice Cream Sandwich (version 4.0) operating system and has a 1.4 GHz quad core processor. It has a 5 megapixel primary camera that facilitates LED flash auto focus shot modes and photo effects. The media player in this tablet can play all the common file formats. Connectivity options in this tablet include built-in Bluetooth USB 2.0 Wi-Fi and HDMI port. It has 16 GB internal storage which is expandable up to 32 GB.
